:: Pool [nobr location]
<<set $gamelocation to "Pool">>

The smell of chlorine entered your nose before you saw the pool area. On the side was a hottub. There was also the entrance to the showers.

<br>
Unfortunately a astral barrier blocks the way forward, with the words "THIS AREA IS A WORK IN PROGESS"
